data.description: Welcome home to this lovingly maintained 25 single family home in the gated Chinquapin Oaks area of The Traditions neighborhood. Filled with light as a result of the many large windows throughout, the open floorplan kitchen and living area are flooded with gorgeous natural light throughout the day. If you love to be part of the action while in the kitchen, this home is FOR YOU! Add to that the expansive covered back patio, and you have an entertainer's dream. The large primary suite boasts an oversized bedroom and large bathroom containing two closets, separate shower and tub, and enclosed water closet. Terrazzo floors in the common areas and large circular vaulted entryways give this home a very unique and impressive style. Two additional bedrooms (one with an ensuite bathroom) will give your guests their own unique oasis as well. Schedule some time to take a look at this beautiful Traditions home before its gone!
